'''City Group''' ({{lang-bn|সিটি গ্রুপ }}) is one of the largest [[Bangladesh]]i [[conglomerate (company)|conglomerates]]. It began on 6 February 1972 as a mustard oil company venture under the name City Oil Mills. The first project of City Oil Mills turned out to be very successful. After then, the company grew very quickly. It presently owns more than 23 major concerns located throughout [[Bangladesh]]. Now City Group stands as one of top ten business houses in Bangladesh.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.jamunabankbd.com/front/others/222|title=Jamuna Bank Ltd.|website=www.jamunabankbd.com|access-date=2016-10-29}}</ref>
== History == City Group was established by [[Fazlur Rahman (Businessman)|Fazlur Rahman]], a business magnate in the private sector of Bangladesh. City Group began on 6 February 1972 as a mustard oil company venture.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.citygroup.com.bd/Content.php?pageType=Corporate&id=15&pId=1&Type=1&PageId=1|title=City Group : Timeline|website=www.citygroup.com.bd|access-date=2016-10-29}}</ref> After its first successful project, City Group invested in new fields,including [[manufacturing]], [[industry]] and [[Trade|trading]]. More enterprises were established in the early 1990s; these included consumer goods, foods, steel, printing & packaging, shipping, power and energy, shares and securities, insurance, media, and healthcare.<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://www.thefinancialexpress-bd.com/more.php?page=detail_news&date=2012-07-24&news_id=137750 |title=Bottled soybean oil up, as refiners renege on promises |publisher=Thefinancialexpress-bd.com |date=2012-07-24 |accessdate=2013-10-20}}</ref>
==List of companies== '''City Group''' now operates over 23 major concerns: * City Oil Mills<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.citygroup.com.bd/Content_Wide.php?pageType=Concerns&id=26&pId=0&Type=1&PageId=26&showType=All|title=City Group : Concerns|website=www.citygroup.com.bd|access-date=2016-10-29}}</ref> * City Re-rolling Mills * City Vegetable Oil Mills Ltd. * City Fibers Ltd. * Hasan Plastic Industries Ltd. * Hasan Flour Mills Ltd. * Hasan Printing & Packaging Ltd. * Hasan Containers Ltd. * City Navigations Ltd. * City PET Industries Ltd. * Shampa Oil Mills Ltd. * City Dal Mills Ltd. * Farzana Oil Refineries Ltd. * VOTT Oil Refineries Ltd. * City Feed Products Ltd. * Deepa Food Products Ltd. * City Seed Crushing Industries Ltd. * City Salt Industries Ltd. * City Sugar Industries Ltd. * C.S.I Power & Energy Ltd. * Rahman Synthetics Ltd. * Hamida Plastic Industries Ltd. * Shampa Flour Mills Ltd. * Hasan Securities Ltd. * City Bran Oil Ltd. * Dhaka Insurance Ltd.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dhakainsurancebd.com/Founder-Chairman|title=View Chairman|website=www.dhakainsurancebd.com|access-date=2016-10-29}}</ref> * Somoy Media Ltd.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.islamibankbd.com/news.php?ID=134|title=Islami Bank Bangladesh Ltd: News & Events|website=www.islamibankbd.com|access-date=2016-10-29}}</ref> * Asgar Ali Hospital Ltd. * New Sagurnal Tea Co. Ltd. Juri, Moulovibazar. * Nahar Tea Estate, Sreemongal, Moulovibazar. * Chandpur Belgaon Tea estate, Banskhali, Chittagram.
